00:26:55,932 --> 00:26:58,752
Stay one day and come back tomorrow.

363
00:27:01,672 --> 00:27:05,512
When you see Xiao Ye, don't talk about studying.

364
00:27:06,212 --> 00:27:07,892
What's wrong?

365
00:27:07,892 --> 00:27:12,312
He's being pushed so hard by your parents that he's freaking out.

366
00:27:12,312 --> 00:27:15,792
They push him to get high scores and to get into medical school.

367
00:27:15,792 --> 00:27:19,532
I'm afraid something bad is going to happen.

368
00:27:19,532 --> 00:27:22,752
Take him for a break. Don't stress him out.

369
00:27:22,752 --> 00:27:25,572
Let him relax, you know?

370
00:27:25,572 --> 00:27:30,912
Okay. Enjoy the dinner. I'm going now.

371
00:27:38,572 --> 00:27:41,352
